text: Initial thoughts on Captain America Brave New World: I liked it overall. Red Hulk was cool and the story was good, but the final fight felt off. Sam Wilson is still human and there's no way he can match a Hulk. The serum debate dragged. Old MCU callbacks didn’t land for me. 7/10
